English
===================

MP3 Download here:   http://kiwi6.com/file/u2mt37ipvj

===================

This is my new work, before i really step into the area of game & movie soundtrack making. i will keep trying to post my new works to increase my skills

This "Earth & Pioneeer" is a suite i created, all music in it are composed for gameplay as background music, you can try it when you have your game time to see how it fit.

This suite every music piece are composed for gameplay such as "Minecraft"and "Age of Mythology". and i'm very thankful that my friend NekoKevin drew this amazing artwork for this music piece. you can follow his more artwork by this link

NekoKevin's DeviantArt:  http://nekokevin.deviantart.com/

Enjoy it, and if you do. please leave the comment,like it and share it to your friends. and don't forget to suscribe it.thank you

Sean.M

中文
===================

MP3 開放下載於此:   http://kiwi6.com/file/u2mt37ipvj

===================

大家好，我又來發表新作了
為了能夠完全的踏入電影與遊戲配樂的專業領域，我會努力的增進自己的技藝，希望大家喜歡我的作品給予支持

這次是一個配樂組曲，顧名思義這組曲裡所有的音樂都是為遊戲而設計的背景音樂，而這是我第一個配樂組曲─「大地與拓荒者」您聽到的這是第一首─「歷史的曙光」是為了Minecraft和「世紀帝國：神話世紀」的遊戲畫面而配的配樂，如果可以你可以邊玩邊聽看看有沒有夠味

還有這影片的圖是我好朋友─青焰兄特地畫的，謝謝他費心，你可以看他的DA來看他更多作品

青焰的DeviantArt：  http://nekokevin.deviantart.com/

如果你喜歡，請記得喜歡、留評論、分享給別人和訂閱頻道，謝謝您

親王
